      "body_lines": [
        "Jayantha de Silva has been appointed Secretary to the Ministry of Technology by President Gotabhaya Rajapaksa today (30).",
        "The letter of appointment was handed over to Jayantha de Silva by Secretary to the President Gamini Senarath at the President's House, Fort, Colombo."
